# 4. Wiring Diagram

## Soil Sensor

* VCC → 3.3V
* GND → GND
* AO → GPIO34

## Relay Module

* VCC → 5V
* GND → GND
* IN → GPIO26

## Push Button

* One side → GPIO27
* Other side → GND
* Configured with `INPUT_PULLUP`

## LED

* Anode → GPIO2 through 220Ω resistor
* Cathode → GND

## Solenoid Valve

* Valve Positive → External Supply +
* Valve Negative → Relay NO
* Relay COM → Supply −

