# 7. Control Logic

Main loop sequence:

1. Read analog soil value
2. Convert to moisture percentage
3. Check button input
4. Process auto/manual mode
5. Update relay and LED
6. Process serial commands
7. Upload telemetry
8. Delay 3 seconds

Pseudo flow:

```text
Read Sensor
   ↓
Check Manual Mode?
   ↓
YES → Keep Manual State
NO  → Compare Threshold
   ↓
Control Relay
   ↓
Upload Telemetry
```

